#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:1
msgid "预备知识"
msgstr "Prerequisites"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:3
msgid ""
"受限玻尔兹曼机（Restricted Boltzmann Machine）是一种基于能量的概率图模型，由可见层（Visible "
"Layer）和隐层（Hidden Layer）组成，层内无连接，层间全连接。 其核心是通过无监督学习学习数据的潜在特征分布。"
msgstr ""
"A Restricted Boltzmann Machine (RBM) is an energy-based probabilistic "
"graphical model composed of a visible layer and a hidden layer, with no "
"intra-layer connections but full inter-layer connections.  Its core idea "
"is to learn the latent feature distribution of data through unsupervised "
"learning."

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:7
msgid "1. 神经网络基础"
msgstr "1\\. Neural Network Basics"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:9
msgid "1.1 神经元模型"
msgstr "1.1 Neuron Model"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:11
#, python-brace-format
msgid "人工神经元是神经网络的基本计算单元。给定输入向量 $\\mathbf{x} \\in \\mathbb{R}^n$，其输出为："
msgstr ""
"The artificial neuron is the basic computing unit of a neural network. "
"Given an input vector $\\mathbf{x} \\in \\mathbb{R}^n$, its output is:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:13
#, fuzzy, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"a = \\phi\\left( \\mathbf{w}^\\top \\mathbf{x} + b \\right)\n"
"\n"
msgstr "a = \\phi\\left( \\mathbf{w}^\\top \\mathbf{x} + b \\right)"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:18
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"其中 $\\mathbf{w} \\in \\mathbb{R}^n$ 为权重向量，$b \\in \\mathbb{R}$ "
"为偏置项，$\\phi(\\cdot)$ 为激活函数。在概率生成模型中，常用 Sigmoid 激活函数："
msgstr ""
"where $\\mathbf{w} \\in \\mathbb{R}^n$ is the weight vector, $b \\in "
"\\mathbb{R}$ is the bias term, and $\\phi(\\cdot)$ is the activation "
"function.  In probabilistic generative models the Sigmoid activation is "
"commonly used:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:20
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"\\sigma(z) = \\frac{1}{1 + e^{-z}}\n"
"\n"
msgstr "\\sigma(z) = \\frac{1}{1 + e^{-z}}"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:25
msgid "1.2 基于能量的模型"
msgstr "1.2 Energy-Based Models"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:27
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"与前馈网络不同，能量基模型（Energy-Based Models, EBMs）通过一个标量能量函数 $E(\\mathbf{x}; "
"\\theta)$ 定义数据的概率分布："
msgstr ""
"Unlike feed-forward networks, Energy-Based Models (EBMs) define a "
"probability distribution over data through a scalar energy function "
"$E(\\mathbf{x}; \\theta)$:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:29
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"P(\\mathbf{x}; \\theta) = \\frac{\\exp(-E(\\mathbf{x}; "
"\\theta))}{Z(\\theta)}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"P(\\mathbf{x}; \\theta) = \\frac{\\exp(-E(\\mathbf{x}; "
"\\theta))}{Z(\\theta)}"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:34
msgid "其中配分函数（partition function）:"
msgstr "where the partition function is:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:36
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"Z(\\theta) = \\sum_{\\mathbf{x}} \\exp(-E(\\mathbf{x}; \\theta))\n"
"\n"
msgstr "Z(\\theta) = \\sum_{\\mathbf{x}} \\exp(-E(\\mathbf{x}; \\theta))"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:41
msgid "确保概率归一化。低能量状态对应高概率。"
msgstr ""
"It ensures proper normalization.  States with lower energy correspond to "
"higher probability."

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:45
msgid "2. 玻尔兹曼机结构"
msgstr "2\\. Boltzmann Machine Structure"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:47
msgid "可见层（**v**）：输入数据的显式表示（如像素值）。"
msgstr ""
"Visible layer (**v**): the explicit representation of input data (e.g. "
"pixel values)."

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:48
msgid "隐藏层（**h**）：提取的潜在特征。"
msgstr "Hidden layer (**h**): extracted latent features."

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:49
msgid "权重矩阵（**w**）：连接可见层与隐层的权重。"
msgstr "Weight matrix (**w**): weights connecting visible and hidden layers."

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:50
msgid "偏置：可见层偏置（**b**）和隐层偏置（**c**）。"
msgstr "Biases: visible-layer bias (**b**) and hidden-layer bias (**c**)."

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:52
msgid "玻尔兹曼机（BM)的拓扑结构是全连接的，而受限玻尔兹曼机通过去掉了可见层和隐藏层内部的链接， 让Gibbs采样的过程更加高效。"
msgstr ""
"A Boltzmann Machine (BM) is fully connected, whereas the Restricted "
"Boltzmann Machine removes intra-layer connections, making Gibbs sampling "
"far more efficient."

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:55
msgid "由于 RBM 的受限结构，隐变量在给定可见变量时相互独立，其条件概率为："
msgstr ""
"Thanks to the restricted structure, hidden variables are mutually "
"independent given the visible variables, with conditional probability:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:57
#, fuzzy, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"P(h_j = 1 \\mid \\mathbf{v}) = \\sigma\\left( \\sum_i w_{ij} v_i + c_j "
"\\right)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"P(h_j = 1 \\mid \\mathbf{v}) = \\sigma\\left( \\sum_i w_{ij} v_i + c_j "
"\\right)"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:62
msgid "同理，"
msgstr "Similarly,"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:64
#, fuzzy, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"P(v_i = 1 \\mid \\mathbf{h}) = \\sigma\\left( \\sum_j w_{ij} h_j + b_i "
"\\right)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"P(v_i = 1 \\mid \\mathbf{h}) = \\sigma\\left( \\sum_j w_{ij} h_j + b_i "
"\\right)"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:69
msgid "3. 能量函数与概率分布"
msgstr "3\\. Energy Function and Probability Distribution"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:71
msgid "3.1 能量函数"
msgstr "3.1 Energy Function"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:73
msgid "RBM 的能量函数定义为："
msgstr "The RBM energy function is defined as:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:75
#, fuzzy, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"E(\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h}) = -\\mathbf{v}^T \\mathbf{W} \\mathbf{h} - "
"\\mathbf{b}^T \\mathbf{v} - \\mathbf{c}^T \\mathbf{h}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"E(\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h}) = -\\mathbf{v}^T \\mathbf{W} \\mathbf{h} - "
"\\mathbf{b}^T \\mathbf{v} - \\mathbf{c}^T \\mathbf{h}"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:80
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"其中，$\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h}$ 分别是可见层和隐层的状态，$\\mathbf{W}$ "
"是连接的权重，$\\mathbf{b}, \\mathbf{c}$ 是一次项系数。"
msgstr ""
"where $\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h}$ are the states of the visible and hidden"
" layers, $\\mathbf{W}$ is the connection weight matrix, and $\\mathbf{b},"
" \\mathbf{c}$ are the first-order coefficients."

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:82
msgid "联合概率分布通过玻尔兹曼分布给出："
msgstr "The joint probability distribution is given by the Boltzmann distribution:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:84
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"P(\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h}) = \\frac{e^{-E(\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h})}}{Z}"
"\n"
"\n"
msgstr "P(\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h}) = \\frac{e^{-E(\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h})}}{Z}"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:89
msgid "其中 $Z$ 为配分函数（归一化因子）。可见层的边缘分布为："
msgstr ""
"where $Z$ is the partition function (normalization factor).  The marginal"
" distribution over the visible layer is:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:91
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"P(\\mathbf{v}) = \\sum_{\\mathbf{h}} P(\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h})\n"
"\n"
msgstr "P(\\mathbf{v}) = \\sum_{\\mathbf{h}} P(\\mathbf{v}, \\mathbf{h})"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:96
msgid "通过最大化似然函数学习参数 $W,b,c$ 。目标函数为负对数似然："
msgstr ""
"Parameters $W,b,c$ are learned by maximizing the likelihood.  The "
"objective is the negative log-likelihood:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:98
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"\\mathcal{L} = -\\sum_{\\mathbf{v}} \\log P(\\mathbf{v})\n"
"\n"
msgstr "\\mathcal{L} = -\\sum_{\\mathbf{v}} \\log P(\\mathbf{v})"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:103
msgid "采用对比散度（CD）算法近似梯度，更新规则为："
msgstr ""
"Contrastive Divergence (CD) is used to approximate the gradient; the "
"update rule is:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:105
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"\\Delta W_{ij} = \\epsilon \\left( \\langle v_i h_j "
"\\rangle_{\\text{data}} - \\langle v_i h_j \\rangle_{\\text{recon}} "
"\\right)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\Delta W_{ij} = \\epsilon \\left( \\langle v_i h_j "
"\\rangle_{\\text{data}} - \\langle v_i h_j \\rangle_{\\text{recon}} "
"\\right)"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:110
msgid ""
"其中 $\\epsilon$ 为学习率，$\\langle \\cdot \\rangle_{\\text{data}}$ 和 $\\langle"
" \\cdot \\rangle_{\\text{recon}}$ 分别为数据分布和重构分布的期望。"
msgstr ""
"where $\\epsilon$ is the learning rate, and $\\langle \\cdot "
"\\rangle_{\\text{data}}$, $\\langle \\cdot \\rangle_{\\text{recon}}$ "
"denote expectations under the data and reconstruction distributions, "
"respectively."

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:112
msgid "3.2 梯度的推导"
msgstr "3.2 Gradient Derivation"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:114
msgid "能量模型的概率可以写成："
msgstr "The probability of an energy model can be written as:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:116
#, fuzzy, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"p(x; \\theta) = \\frac{1}{Z} \\tilde{p}(x; \\theta)\n"
"\n"
msgstr "p(x; \\theta) = \\frac{1}{Z} \\tilde{p}(x; \\theta)"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:121
msgid "其梯度为："
msgstr "Its gradient is:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:123
#, fuzzy, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"\\nabla_\\theta \\log p(x; \\theta) = \\nabla_\\theta \\log \\tilde{p}(x;"
" \\theta) - \\nabla_\\theta \\log Z\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\nabla_\\theta \\log p(x; \\theta) = \\nabla_\\theta \\log \\tilde{p}(x;"
" \\theta) - \\nabla_\\theta \\log Z"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:128
msgid "配分函数的梯度难以直接计算"
msgstr "The gradient of the partition function is hard to compute directly:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:130
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"\\nabla_\\theta \\log Z\n"
"&= \\frac{\\nabla_\\theta Z}{Z} \\\\\n"
"&= \\frac{\\nabla_\\theta \\sum_x \\tilde{p}(x)}{Z} \\\\\n"
"&= \\sum_x \\frac{\\nabla_\\theta \\tilde{p}(x)}{Z}\n"
"\\end{aligned}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:140
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"对于保证所有的 $x$ 都有 $p(x) > 0$ 的模型，我们可以用 $\\exp(\\log \\tilde{p}(x))$ 代替 "
"$\\tilde{p}(x)$。"
msgstr ""
"For models that guarantee $p(x) > 0$ for every $x$, we can replace "
"$\\tilde{p}(x)$ with $\\exp(\\log \\tilde{p}(x))$."

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:142
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"\\frac{\\sum_x \\nabla_\\theta \\exp(\\log \\tilde{p}(x))}{Z}\n"
"&= \\frac{\\sum_x \\exp(\\log \\tilde{p}(x)) \\nabla_\\theta \\log "
"\\tilde{p}(x)}{Z} \\\\\n"
"&= \\frac{\\sum_x \\tilde{p}(x) \\nabla_\\theta \\log \\tilde{p}(x)}{Z} "
"\\\\\n"
"&= \\sum_x p(x) \\nabla_\\theta \\log \\tilde{p}(x) \\\\\n"
"&= \\mathbb{E}_{x \\sim p(x)} \\nabla_\\theta \\log \\tilde{p}(x)\n"
"\\end{aligned}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:153
msgid "综上，"
msgstr "Putting it together,"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:155
#, fuzzy, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
" \\nabla_\\theta \\log p(x; \\theta) = \\nabla_\\theta \\log \\hat{p}(x; "
"\\theta) - \\mathbb{E}_{x \\sim p(x; \\theta)} \\nabla_\\theta \\log "
"\\hat{p}(x; \\theta)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\nabla_\\theta \\log p(x; \\theta) = \\nabla_\\theta \\log \\hat{p}(x; "
"\\theta) - \\mathbb{E}_{x \\sim p(x; \\theta)} \\nabla_\\theta \\log "
"\\hat{p}(x; \\theta)\n"
"\n"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:159
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"第二项中 $p(x; \\theta)$ 实际上是模型预测的 $\\mathbf{x}$ "
"的分布，而训练中的第一项是服从实际的数据的分布的。即上式可以写成"
msgstr ""
"In the second term $p(x; \\theta)$ is the distribution predicted by the "
"model, while the first term in training is under the real data "
"distribution.  Thus the equation can be rewritten as:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:161
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"\\nabla_\\theta \\log p(x; \\theta) = \\mathbb{E}_{x \\sim "
"p_{\\text{data}}} \\nabla_\\theta \\log \\hat{p}(x; \\theta) - "
"\\mathbb{E}_{x \\sim p_{\\text{model}}} \\nabla_\\theta \\log \\hat{p}(x;"
" \\theta)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\nabla_\\theta \\log p(x; \\theta) = \\mathbb{E}_{x \\sim "
"p_{\\text{data}}} \\nabla_\\theta \\log \\hat{p}(x; \\theta) - "
"\\mathbb{E}_{x \\sim p_{\\text{model}}} \\nabla_\\theta \\log \\hat{p}(x;"
" \\theta)\n"
"\n"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:165
msgid "这里我们考虑玻尔兹曼机的能量函数，容易求得"
msgstr "Considering the Boltzmann-machine energy function, we can easily obtain:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:167
#, fuzzy, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"\\nabla_W \\log \\hat{p}(x; W) = v h^\\mathrm{T}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\nabla_W \\log \\hat{p}(x; W) = v h^\\mathrm{T}\n"
"\n"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:171
msgid "只要分别得到 $p_{\\text{data}}$, $p_{\\text{model}}$ 分布下的 $v$ 和 $h$ 的值即可计算梯度。即为："
msgstr ""
"One only needs to obtain the values of $v$ and $h$ under "
"$p_{\\text{data}}$ and $p_{\\text{model}}$ respectively to compute the "
"gradient, namely:"

#: ../../source/getting_started/background.md:174
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"\\Delta W_{ij} = \\epsilon \\left( \\langle v_i h_j "
"\\rangle_{\\text{data}} - \\langle v_i h_j \\rangle_{\\text{recon}} "
"\\right)\n"
msgstr ""
"\\Delta W_{ij} = \\epsilon \\left( \\langle v_i h_j "
"\\rangle_{\\text{data}} - \\langle v_i h_j \\rangle_{\\text{recon}} "
"\\right)"

